OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,6,Ftime this morning. The afternoon will
OL,7,Fbe brighter with a few showers, some
OL,8,Fof these heavy but tending to move
OL,9,Fthrough quickly in brisk southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA rather cloudy night with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain or showers, the showers
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy around western
OL,15,Fcoasts. Winds will be brisk, and
OL,16,Fstrong at times around western coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
